1. *Koristim* ovu mašinu već godinama. (I have been using this machine for years.)
2. Ona *koristi* moje ideje. (She uses my ideas.)
3. *Koristio* sam ga još uvek. (I had been still using it.)
4. Šta *koristiš* za svoju prehranu? (What do you use for your diet?)
5. Oni *koriste* svoje vreme za putovanja. (They use their time for travelling.)